message: Cleaning up my user page.
Removed useless information that takes up space preventing this page from being as efficient as it can be.
Included all major faiths in religion section to better inform people who come to this page for information on the English.

Hi my previous edit was removed, only did it because after looking at many other countries with much higher Muslim populations nowhere in religions is Islam specifically mentioned, it is not as if I am purposefully trying to exclude them but it is kind of useless and unnecessary information which is already included in the link to religion in the U.K. \nkind regards sorry if any offence was taken.
